name: Experiment Or Die #83
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The Cool Alphabet is going to be word replacements for the standard run of the mill alphabet. I'm around the right age that I COULD have seen Return Of The Jedi in the theater, but I didn't, but I do remember it being the first Star Wars movie I saw and I loved everything about it. Especially the Ewoks. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
